### Description [Feature Request only]

Signal Graph shows usages of signals in templates but not host binding 

```
@Component({
  selector: 'icon',
  template: `<svg-icon [applyClass]="true" [name]="icon()" [svgStyle]="{ 'width.em': 1, 'height.em': 1 }" class="icon"></svg-icon>`,
  styleUrls: ['./icon.component.scss'],
  changeDetection: ChangeDetectionStrategy.OnPush,
  imports: [AngularSvgIconModule],
  host: {
    '[class.icon-large]': 'size() === "large"',
    '[style.--icon-size]': 'iconSizeValue()'
  }
})
export class IconComponent {
  public icon = input.required<Icon>();
  public size = input<IconSize>();
  public customSize = input<number>();

  protected iconSizeValue = computed( () => isNumber(this.customSize()) ? `${pxToRem(this.customSize()!)}rem` : undefined)

  }
```

produces 

